content.rendered:
Naval commando James Reece’s (Chris Pratt) unit is ambushed during a risky covert mission. Reece returns home to his family, but his memories are conflicted about the event and his own guilt. However, as new evidence comes to light, Reece realizes that dark forces are working against him, and that not only his life is in danger, but also the lives of those he loves.

Number of seasons: 1 (2022- )

Status: Ongoing

Channel: Amazon

Starring: Chris Pratt, Taylor Kitsch, Constance Wu
